WEBVTT

00:00:19.162 --> 00:00:24.350
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:25.662
♪Because you exist♪

00:00:25.662 --> 00:00:27.662
♪You're always♪

00:00:27.742 --> 00:00:32.392
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:00:32.392 --> 00:00:35.125
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:00:35.125 --> 00:00:36.645
♪Hold tight♪

00:00:36.692 --> 00:00:42.412
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:00:42.482 --> 00:00:47.600
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 9=

00:00:54.699 --> 00:00:56.059
Have you met Mr. Hong?

00:00:56.900 --> 00:00:57.500
Miss Yan,

00:00:58.619 --> 00:01:00.699
I've reinstalled the system
in the control room.

00:01:00.939 --> 00:01:03.220
The issues you had before
shouldn't happen again.

00:01:03.460 --> 00:01:04.499
Thank you, Captain Shen.

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:11.779
How did it go with the collaboration?

00:01:12.259 --> 00:01:13.499
I met Hong in person.

00:01:14.020 --> 00:01:14.859
But

00:01:14.859 --> 00:01:16.380
he hasn't agreed to work with me yet.

00:01:18.940 --> 00:01:19.900
Is he

00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:22.380
really as quirky and hard to deal with

00:01:22.380 --> 00:01:23.300
as people say?

00:01:24.300 --> 00:01:25.619
Well,

00:01:26.460 --> 00:01:28.300
his temper is a little unusual.

00:01:28.900 --> 00:01:29.940
But he's an artist.

00:01:29.940 --> 00:01:31.259
Having some personality is normal.

00:01:32.259 --> 00:01:33.380
Actually,

00:01:33.779 --> 00:01:35.859
Hong is quite interesting.

00:01:36.300 --> 00:01:37.820
He's very much like I imagined.

00:01:38.259 --> 00:01:39.619
Unique personality.

00:01:40.740 --> 00:01:43.100
No wonder his paintings
are so distinctive.

00:01:45.339 --> 00:01:46.339
Now I just hope

00:01:46.339 --> 00:01:47.979
he'll take a good look
at my proposal.

00:01:48.540 --> 00:01:49.540
Although

00:01:49.660 --> 00:01:51.580
we've only met once this time,

00:01:51.779 --> 00:01:52.660
maybe next time

00:01:52.900 --> 00:01:54.820
there'll be a chance to work together.

00:01:54.820 --> 00:01:56.740
(This girl is pretty interesting.)

00:02:02.540 --> 00:02:05.100
(I'm praising Mr. Hong.
Why is he smiling like that?)

00:02:05.419 --> 00:02:06.219
Let's go.

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:17.719
(Boss,)

00:02:18.860 --> 00:02:21.260
(since you don't want Ms. Mu to know
who you are,)

00:02:21.260 --> 00:02:24.420
(why show up like that and even help her
with the appraisal report?)

00:02:25.580 --> 00:02:27.300
(We're partners, that's all.)

00:02:27.499 --> 00:02:28.939
(Helping her is helping myself.)

00:02:30.939 --> 00:02:32.460
But I think

00:02:32.700 --> 00:02:34.099
you like her.

00:02:39.262 --> 00:02:40.898
(You like her.)

00:03:01.900 --> 00:03:03.099
Would I

00:03:03.180 --> 00:03:04.860
fall for a girl like Mu Zhiyu?

00:03:11.140 --> 00:03:13.059
(Do I really...)

00:03:14.140 --> 00:03:16.059
Didn't you say boxing
isn't about hitting people?

00:03:16.619 --> 00:03:17.499
Look at you now.

00:03:17.659 --> 00:03:19.339
You look like
you're about to kill someone.

00:03:33.140 --> 00:03:33.939
Come practice.

00:03:34.900 --> 00:03:35.740
Let's see

00:03:35.740 --> 00:03:37.059
if you remember what I taught you.

00:03:52.939 --> 00:03:53.819
Shen Jibai,

00:03:54.339 --> 00:03:55.300
is your job

00:03:55.460 --> 00:03:56.499
dangerous?

00:04:02.059 --> 00:04:03.260
Actually, these scars

00:04:03.659 --> 00:04:05.260
aren't from
when I worked as a bodyguard.

00:04:07.460 --> 00:04:08.900
They're from boxing.

00:04:09.180 --> 00:04:10.180
Punch him!

00:04:10.180 --> 00:04:11.619
Get up!

00:04:11.740 --> 00:04:12.420
Beat him to death!

00:04:14.219 --> 00:04:15.740
You think you can trust people

00:04:15.740 --> 00:04:16.979
and make friends with them?

00:04:19.580 --> 00:04:20.219
Punch him!

00:04:20.419 --> 00:04:21.299
Beat him to death!

00:04:22.299 --> 00:04:24.099
But they took the money
they bet on your match

00:04:24.140 --> 00:04:25.299
and ran off with it.

00:04:26.140 --> 00:04:26.940
Shut up.

00:04:28.659 --> 00:04:31.060
Did you forget
how you were bought to fight?

00:04:31.339 --> 00:04:32.299
It was your mom!

00:04:32.339 --> 00:04:32.820
Stop it!

00:04:32.820 --> 00:04:34.099
She sold you to the fight club.

00:04:35.979 --> 00:04:36.859
So,

00:04:37.099 --> 00:04:38.779
you unwanted trash,

00:04:39.419 --> 00:04:40.820
why are you so proud?

00:04:40.859 --> 00:04:41.900
Why?

00:04:42.339 --> 00:04:42.820
I...

00:04:42.820 --> 00:04:45.900
You're definitely going to lose today.
I told you to shut up.

00:04:47.500 --> 00:04:48.099
Jeez.

00:04:48.539 --> 00:04:49.219
No way.

00:04:49.219 --> 00:04:50.460
- Why are you so slow?
- Get up.

00:04:50.460 --> 00:04:51.739
Get up!

00:04:51.739 --> 00:04:52.539
Up!

00:04:52.539 --> 00:04:53.779
Come on. Can you do it or not?

00:04:53.779 --> 00:04:56.060
Get up now!

00:04:58.260 --> 00:05:00.659
Shen Jibai, you won this round.

00:05:00.900 --> 00:05:02.339
This is your reward.

00:05:06.779 --> 00:05:07.659
Shen Jibai.

00:05:09.820 --> 00:05:10.739
Are you alright?

00:05:40.820 --> 00:05:42.299
Throw your punches with force.

00:05:42.940 --> 00:05:45.339
Imagine the thing in front of you
is your enemy.

00:05:46.940 --> 00:05:50.140
Gather all your anger and hatred
and strike a killing blow.

00:06:05.575 --> 00:06:09.025
♪Ten years of the past
have turned to smoke♪

00:06:09.615 --> 00:06:12.585
♪I close my innocent eyes♪

00:06:12.955 --> 00:06:15.775
♪No more parting by life or death♪

00:06:16.145 --> 00:06:19.445
♪Only mourning remains in my heart♪

00:06:21.545 --> 00:06:25.195
♪Deeply trapped in
a vortex of mysteries♪

00:06:25.605 --> 00:06:28.775
♪Wading through the muddy waters
of hearts and times♪

00:06:29.675 --> 00:06:32.775
♪Returning from the ashes
to craft the plan♪

00:06:32.900 --> 00:06:35.612
♪From now on, no one can break it♪

00:06:37.665 --> 00:06:42.845
♪Love has vanished, hatred is spreading♪

00:06:45.705 --> 00:06:48.095
♪Ignoring the arrangements of fate♪

00:06:48.095 --> 00:06:51.135
♪Only following my own will♪

00:06:53.575 --> 00:06:56.095
♪After a familiar embrace♪

00:06:56.095 --> 00:07:00.155
♪The world's turmoil
is still hard to discern♪

00:07:00.155 --> 00:07:03.087
♪The green flower breaks in two♪

00:07:03.825 --> 00:07:07.762
♪Our hearts will be together at last♪

00:07:08.637 --> 00:07:13.117
♪Waking up between our dreams♪

00:07:13.117 --> 00:07:17.175
♪Drawing a circle of falling blossoms♪

00:07:17.175 --> 00:07:21.040
♪The ripples in my heart begin
only because of you♪

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:25.237
♪Every move on the chessboard
is a cruel trial♪

00:07:25.237 --> 00:07:27.700
♪The course of fate
is written by our own hands♪

00:07:27.700 --> 00:07:28.539
I told you

00:07:28.539 --> 00:07:30.140
to stay focus when you box.

00:07:30.237 --> 00:07:33.300
♪Yet at first sight, I fell for you♪

00:07:34.020 --> 00:07:35.140
It's getting late.

00:07:35.339 --> 00:07:36.219
Rest up early.

00:07:37.100 --> 00:07:40.339
♪A destined bond in this life
is worth a lifetime♪

00:07:40.339 --> 00:07:41.179
Wait.

00:07:44.219 --> 00:07:45.700
There's something I want to tell you.

00:07:48.299 --> 00:07:49.539
I've thought it through.

00:07:50.659 --> 00:07:52.299
About the scandal,

00:07:52.739 --> 00:07:54.620
Hong's appraisal alone
may not be enough,

00:07:55.180 --> 00:07:57.199
we need proof
that those men in black attacked people

00:07:57.199 --> 00:07:58.580
and tried to steal the painting.

00:08:00.060 --> 00:08:01.620
We checked earlier.

00:08:02.179 --> 00:08:04.260
The surveillance cameras covering
the parking lot area

00:08:04.260 --> 00:08:05.539
were deliberately damaged.

00:08:05.900 --> 00:08:08.260
Xu Mingzhu must've arranged it in advance.

00:08:12.219 --> 00:08:13.219
Dashcam.

00:08:13.900 --> 00:08:16.380
Right. Dashcam from nearby cars.

00:08:17.179 --> 00:08:18.500
I'll find a way to check them.

00:08:25.099 --> 00:08:27.339
There was a family car
parked directly across from the scene.

00:08:27.620 --> 00:08:29.339
This is the dashcam memory card.

00:08:32.579 --> 00:08:34.480
(Dashcam)
Hopefully, there's something useful in it.

00:08:36.579 --> 00:08:37.860
There's nothing here.

00:08:39.059 --> 00:08:39.900
Looks like

00:08:39.900 --> 00:08:41.740
Xu Mingzhu prepared for this.

00:08:42.020 --> 00:08:43.819
The footage was deleted.

00:08:54.860 --> 00:08:55.459
Leave it to me.

00:08:55.500 --> 00:08:56.380
I have a way.

00:08:57.699 --> 00:08:58.380
Ms. Xu,

00:08:58.819 --> 00:08:59.699
this memory card

00:08:59.699 --> 00:09:01.380
came from the dashcam at the scene.

00:09:01.659 --> 00:09:02.699
I brought it back for you.

00:09:06.100 --> 00:09:08.459
How did this memory card
end up with you?

00:09:08.500 --> 00:09:09.340
To be honest,

00:09:09.340 --> 00:09:11.059
I got it from Mu Zhiyu.

00:09:11.939 --> 00:09:13.659
(But Zhao Ye already deleted everything)

00:09:13.900 --> 00:09:15.699
(from this card.)

00:09:18.100 --> 00:09:18.740
Zhao Ye,

00:09:19.340 --> 00:09:21.100
did you finish what I asked you to do?

00:09:21.140 --> 00:09:22.380
Did you delete everything?

00:09:22.860 --> 00:09:24.260
I deleted everything on the card.

00:09:24.659 --> 00:09:25.740
Just like you ordered,

00:09:25.740 --> 00:09:27.419
I kept a backup on my computer.

00:09:27.900 --> 00:09:28.939
(So)

00:09:28.939 --> 00:09:30.819
(there's a backup
on Zhao Ye's computer.)

00:09:34.900 --> 00:09:36.020
Ms. Mu's here.

00:09:36.020 --> 00:09:37.620
We have a few questions for you.

00:09:38.140 --> 00:09:38.900
Sorry.

00:09:38.900 --> 00:09:40.459
Ms. Mu isn't accepting questions
right now.

00:09:40.459 --> 00:09:41.380
Please let us through.

00:09:41.500 --> 00:09:42.299
Ms. Mu,

00:09:42.340 --> 00:09:43.340
there are rumors saying

00:09:43.340 --> 00:09:45.819
you deliberately damaged
Hong's painting to profit from it.

00:09:45.939 --> 00:09:47.659
How do you respond?

00:09:48.060 --> 00:09:50.440
There are also reports saying
that because of this incident,

00:09:50.440 --> 00:09:52.740
the Mu Group board wants you
to step down from your position.

00:09:52.740 --> 00:09:53.779
Is that true?

00:09:56.380 --> 00:09:58.659
(Looks like Xu Mingzhu
sent these reporters.)

00:09:58.659 --> 00:10:00.000
(Good thing I came prepared.)

00:10:01.819 --> 00:10:03.539
(Let's see how you handle this now.)

00:10:04.299 --> 00:10:05.220
Everyone, please look.

00:10:06.220 --> 00:10:08.380
This is the footage from the scene
that day.

00:10:09.220 --> 00:10:10.719
You can clearly see in the video

00:10:10.719 --> 00:10:12.800
a group of men in black
trying to steal the painting.

00:10:12.939 --> 00:10:14.340
They even threatened me with knives.

00:10:15.220 --> 00:10:17.740
So I'd like to ask,
who would be so stupid enough

00:10:17.900 --> 00:10:20.179
to risk it all
just to stage something like that?

00:10:21.179 --> 00:10:22.740
(Where did she get the footage?)

00:10:22.819 --> 00:10:24.020
This video alone

00:10:24.020 --> 00:10:26.299
doesn't prove what really happened.

00:10:26.299 --> 00:10:28.740
If you staged the whole thing yourself,

00:10:28.740 --> 00:10:29.939
it would be hard to verify.

00:10:32.260 --> 00:10:34.020
(You're no match for me.)

00:10:34.020 --> 00:10:34.980
I can prove it.

00:10:45.962 --> 00:10:49.872
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:10:50.332 --> 00:10:54.432
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:10:54.702 --> 00:10:58.872
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:11:03.412 --> 00:11:07.352
♪Shadows move around♪

00:11:07.352 --> 00:11:11.962
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:11:11.962 --> 00:11:16.172
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:11:20.092 --> 00:11:25.562
♪Don't slip away♪

00:11:28.332 --> 00:11:32.902
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:32.902 --> 00:11:37.202
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:37.302 --> 00:11:41.302
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:41.642 --> 00:11:45.302
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:46.092 --> 00:11:50.342
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:50.402 --> 00:11:54.642
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:54.732 --> 00:11:58.942
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:59.042 --> 00:12:04.872
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪